%= pfc_nf(+In,-Out) maps the LHR of a pfc rule In to one normal form 
%= Out.  It also does certain optimizations.  Backtracking into this
%= predicate will produce additional clauses.


pfc_nf(LHS,List) :-
  pfc_nf1(LHS,List2),
