%   File   : pfcjust.pl
%   Author : Tim Finin, finin@prc.unisys.com
%   Author :  Dave Matuszek, dave@prc.unisys.com
%   Updated:
%   Purpose: predicates for accessing Pfc Justifications.
%   Status: more or less working.
